<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape     id="_x0000_s1289" type="#_x0000_t202" style='position:absolute;left:18pt;     top:233.25pt;width:543pt;height:597.75pt;z-index:56;mso-wrap-distance-left:2.88pt;     mso-wrap-distance-top:2.88pt;mso-wrap-distance-right:2.88pt;     mso-wrap-distance-bottom:2.88pt' filled="f" fillcolor="aqua [7]" stroked="f"     strokecolor="black [0]" o:cliptowrap="t">     <v:fill color2="aqua [7]"/>     <v:stroke color2="aqua [7]">      <o:left v:ext="view" color="black [0]" color2="aqua [7]"/>      <o:top v:ext="view" color="black [0]" color2="aqua [7]"/>      <o:right v:ext="view" color="black [0]" color2="aqua [7]"/>      <o:bottom v:ext="view" color="black [0]" color2="aqua [7]"/>      <o:column v:ext="view" color="black [0]" color2="aqua [7]"/>     </v:stroke>     <v:shadow color="#ccc [4]"/>     <v:path insetpenok="f"/>     <v:textbox style='mso-column-margin:2mm' inset="2.88pt,2.88pt,2.88pt,2.88pt"/>    </v:shape><![endif]-->
<!--[if !vml]-->
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td width="724" height="797"><!--[endif]-->
          <div class="style1" v:shape="_x0000_s1289">
            <p align="justify"><strong><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">General Terms</span></strong></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">You  must have a valid&nbsp; account for you to able to purchased the featured  products we offer. You can&nbsp; activate your account once you&rsquo;ve signed in  to register for registration. Once you have activated your account,  simply select the products you wish to purchase just&nbsp; click select.</span></p>
            <p align="justify"><strong><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">Notifications</span></strong></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">The  producer of the&nbsp; every products will send a confirmation of your order  by email when your order is placed.&nbsp; The transaction of the products is  directly to the producer. The developer of the system will ONLY serves&nbsp;  as the bridge of the consumer to the producers. The confirmation will  include all product pricing, applicable taxes, and shipping charges as  shown on your order prior to submission. Once the order has shipped, a  shipment notice that is also your invoice will be sent via email. Be  sure to print or save your email shipment notification/invoice for your  records.</span></p>
            <p align="justify"><strong><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">PRODUCT SHIPMENT</span></strong></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">The  producer of every products&nbsp; makes every effort to ship your product  according to the estimated lead times provided at the time you place  your order. </span><span lang="en-PH" xml:lang="en-PH">Orders  are normally dispatched on the next business day following the day the  order was confirmed to the customer. Orders for delivery within Luzon  and Mindanao will be delivered within 3 to 5 days from the process date  of the order. Orders to be delivered to a provincial destination within  the Region VIII will take 2 to 3 days from the process date to be  delivered. </span></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">During  peak periods surrounding holidays, there may be an additional 3-5 days  needed to process orders due to volume increases. If your shipment  takes longer than originally estimated, we will let you know via email  and we will make every effort to complete your order as quickly as  possible. Once your order has shipped, a shipment notification/invoice  will be sent via email. </span></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">Lead  times are represented as business days (Monday thru Friday) and exclude  major holidays. For the shipment of the product it will depends on the  agreement of the producer and the consumer of what manner of the  delivery will take place.</span></p>
            <p align="justify"><strong><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">CANCELLATIONS</span></strong></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">Please  review your order carefully before submitting. Once submitted, our  automated processing will send your order into production after 90  minutes and we will be unable to make changes or cancel your order.  Within this 90-minute period, you may cancel your order.</span></p>
            <p align="justify"><strong><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">SALES AND DISTRIBUTION</span></strong></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">This  site is a bridge of the consumers to its manufacturer/producers of the  product they purchased. The selling of the products is within the  Philippines Archipelago only. </span></p>
            <p align="justify"><strong><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">PRICES</span></strong></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">All  prices are in Philippine Peso/currency. The billing for your order will  also be in Philippine Peso/currency, your total order price will  include the price of the product(s) plus any applicable sales tax and  shipping charges. Please review your order carefully prior to  submitting it for processing.</span></p>
            <p align="justify"><strong><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">SALES TAX</span></strong></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">Purchases  will include sales tax based on the ship-to location and the sales tax  rate in effect at the time your order is placed. If the sales tax rate  for the state to which your order is being shipped changes before the  product is shipped, the rate in effect at the time your order was  received in our system will apply. </span></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-PH" xml:lang="en-PH"><strong>RETURNS</strong></span><span lang="en-PH" xml:lang="en-PH"><br />
            If you would like to return an item purchased in this site due to  product defect a replacement or a refund of the purchase amount,  whichever you prefer. </span></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-PH" xml:lang="en-PH"><br />
              Please advice us within seven (7) days from receipt of the item, of  your intent to return an item, including the corresponding reason or  actual product defect, and whether you wish for a replacement or a  refund.&nbsp; If you wish for a replacement, we shall send you a replacement  free of charge within 2-3 days upon receipt of the returned item.</span></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-PH" xml:lang="en-PH">&nbsp;</span></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-PH" xml:lang="en-PH">If you wish for a refund, we shall facilitate the refund provided that:</span></p>
            <p align="justify">A.&nbsp;<span lang="en-PH" xml:lang="en-PH">You return the item in its original delivery condition</span></p>
            <p align="justify">B.&nbsp;<span lang="en-PH" xml:lang="en-PH">Include a copy of the delivery receipt</span></p>
            <p align="justify">C.&nbsp;<span lang="en-PH" xml:lang="en-PH">Return the item within seven (7) days upon receipt of your advice to refund <br />
            </span></p>
            <p align="justify" class="style3"><span lang="en-PH" xml:lang="en-PH">&nbsp;</span><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">QUALITY ASSURANCE</span></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">If  for some reason you are not satisfied with the quality of product you  have received, please email DTI for assistance at dtisamar@yahoo.com If  we determines that a defect occurred in delivery, we will, at its  discretion, credit back or replace the defective items.</span></p>
            <p align="justify"><strong><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">PRIVACY</span></strong></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">We  collect personal information (&ldquo;Personal Information&rdquo;) for the purpose  of fulfilling your request or to provide you with our products,  services and related information.</span></p>
            <p align="justify"><span lang="en-US" xml:lang="en-US">The  Personal Information you submit will be stored in a database that will  be monitored by the DTI personnel. The Personal Information may be  disclosed to our affiliated entities and to third party service  providers to the extent that they need access to your information in  accordance with Sudoy company Privacy Policy found. We will protect  your Personal Information including taking appropriate technical,  organizational, and legal steps to protect your Personal Information.</span></p>
          </div></td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
